Hello World # To create a Hello World plug-in for Eclipse, click: File ➜ New ➜ Other&hellip;
Select Plug-in Project and click Next &gt;
The New Plug-in Project wizard will guide you through the options for creating a new plug-in.
Enter a project name (like HelloWorld), and click Next &gt;
On the Content page, you can set the ID, Version, Name and Vendor of the plug-in.
The Version will be 1.
